        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The system only allows installation of one profile of this type, and it requires installation through a user-approved MDM server. Apps listed in this profile have low-level access to the system, including, but not limited to, key logging and user interface manipulation outside the app’s context.",
